What about `ImBloc` still being `registerLazySingleton`? The review 2 marked thi
s as blocking, but `_onResetRequested` was added to clear all state. Is this eno
ugh? The review says:\n"修复: 在 `ImBloc` 中添加清除方法，并在登出事件中调用；或
